{"tid":1489615,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"郭家麒：將軍澳斬人案有政治目的　製造白色恐怖","createTime":"2019-08-20T02:12:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T02:43:34.000Z","uid":212626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b85d280c9bcc33f83c38e883d73f2957f9160bff","tid":1489615,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:12:59.000Z","msg":"將軍澳連接景林邨和厚德邨的行人隧道凌晨發生持刀傷人案，一男兩女受傷。公民黨立法會議員郭家麒在一個電台節目就此表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">疑犯明顯有政治目的，是製造白色恐怖</span>。<br />\n<br />\n郭家麒指出，警方快速拘捕反修例示威者，並控告暴動罪，但對於7月21日元朗站暴力襲擊事件中被捕的27人，就遲遲未落案起訴，質疑處理手法不對等。<br />\n<br />\n另外，郭家麒表示，收到幾宗個案，有市民過關時被內地人員檢查手機，查看有無反修例示威的相片及影片，昨日已去信政制及內地事務局，希望與局方討論相關事宜，強調內地執法部門除了涉及國家安全，或刑事調查外，無權檢查市民手機，認為做法無法令港人信任中央。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2225073/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2225073%2F&d=OqNKNX3jJWm7Bjx4wMOex8vW%2Fvk9QtnWk1JKGKfj%2Fbg%3D&h=a5712e22\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2225073/</a>"},{"pid":"0f5d927da697215ea2ab611517080dad0386e495","tid":1489615,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:15:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2dc8555157dd623cdee7a578f6336d6bf77c0a2","tid":1489615,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:16:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19cc0da0ff7a2403001d34ce098f9f2c9a65c635","tid":1489615,"uid":68689,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:16:28.000Z","msg":"都已經唔係製造白色恐怖<br />\n係製造恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3e7e1b71638e065fd6d862f0d21ea6e5274e1ca","tid":1489615,"uid":144453,"like":0,"dislike":0,